=head1 DESCRIPTION

Information about a voice recording, chat transcript, or screen
recording.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 DeletionReason => Str

If the recording/transcript was deleted, this is the reason entered for
the deletion.


=head2 FragmentStartNumber => Str

The number that identifies the Kinesis Video Streams fragment where the
customer audio stream started.


=head2 FragmentStopNumber => Str

The number that identifies the Kinesis Video Streams fragment where the
customer audio stream stopped.


=head2 Location => Str

The location, in Amazon S3, for the recording/transcript.


=head2 MediaStreamType => Str

Information about the media stream used during the conversation.


=head2 ParticipantType => Str

Information about the conversation participant, whether they are an
agent or contact. The participant types are as follows:

=over

=item *

All

=item *

Manager

=item *

Agent

=item *

Customer

=item *

Thirdparty

=item *

Supervisor

=back



=head2 StartTimestamp => Str

When the conversation of the last leg of the recording started in UTC
time.


=head2 Status => Str

The status of the recording/transcript.


=head2 StopTimestamp => Str

When the conversation of the last leg of recording stopped in UTC time.


=head2 StorageType => Str

Where the recording/transcript is stored.



